name: EmptyRecycleBinResult

methods.name: getErrors
methods.description: If an error occurred during the delete for this record or sObject, returns a list of one or more Database.Error objects. If no errors occurred, the returned list is empty.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the ID of the record or sObject you attempted to delete.

methods.name: isSuccess
methods.description: Returns true if the record or sObject was successfully removed from the Recycle Bin; otherwise false.

description: The result of the emptyRecycleBin DML operation returned by the Database.emptyRecycleBin method.
